## Evidence factors — Database Query Results

Base: **40**

| Factor | Points | Condition | Weight rationale |
|--------|--------|-----------|-----------------|
| User named environment explicitly | **+20** | DB.0a satisfied — no inference | Wrong env = wrong data; highest weight |
| Query returned results | **+15** | Non-empty result set | Evidence exists |
| Schema/table verified to exist | **+10** | Table confirmed before query | Prevents misleading empty results |
| Query uses standard patterns (DB.2) | **+5** | Follows documented join patterns | Tested patterns reduce query errors |
| Multiple tables cross-referenced | **+5** | ≥2 schema joins for completeness | Richer evidence |
| Environment aligned (Phoenix branch matches DB env) | **+5** | Same env for code + DB | Code-DB consistency |
