## Evidence factors — Playwright Test Run Results (HandsOff sub-step)

Base: **40**

| Factor | Points | Condition | Weight rationale |
|--------|--------|-----------|-----------------|
| All tests passed | **+40** | Pass rate = 100% | Full validation |
| Most tests passed (≥ 80%) | **+30** | Pass rate 80–99% | Strong but incomplete |
| Some tests passed (50–79%) | **+15** | Mixed results | Partial validation |
| Few tests passed (< 50%) | **+0** | Mostly failing | Minimal value |
| No tests passed | **-10** | Pass rate = 0% | Total failure |
| Tests actually executed (not skipped) | **+10** | ≥1 test ran to completion | Execution confirmed |
| Environment stable during run | **+5** | No connection/timeout errors in log | Clean execution |
| Flaky failures detected | **-5** | Same test passes on retry | Unreliable signal |
| Environment errors during run | **-10** | Connection/timeout/500 errors in log | Results may not reflect code behavior |
| Spec validator passed (≥ 80/100) before run | **+5** | Step 4.5 completed | Spec quality assured |

**Pass rate mapping:**

| Pass rate | Score contribution |
|-----------|-------------------|
| 100% | +40 |
| 90–99% | +35 |
| 80–89% | +30 |
| 70–79% | +20 |
| 50–69% | +15 |
| 25–49% | +5 |
| 1–24% | +0 |
| 0% | -10 |

