## Multi-agent aggregation

When a parent agent receives scores from multiple subagents:

| Method | When to use |
|--------|-------------|
| **Minimum** | Pipeline workflows (HandsOff) where all steps must succeed |
| **Weighted average** | Independent parallel results (e.g. PhoenixExpert + DB query) |

Parent MUST show: individual sub-scores + aggregation method + final score.

